- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is another possible category as the paper deals with numerical computations on sparse matrices.

- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses the implications of their approach on core data mining algorithms.
